NK032(khi)007:1: // dpal dpal la gnyis te rtogs pa bdag gi dpal dang /
NK032(khi)007:2: thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal lo //
NK032(khi)007:3: rdo rje sems dpa'i rba sgom gyi gsung rdo rje'i
NK032(khi)007:4: ni don chos nyid kyi rdo rje 'dus ma byas
NK032(khi)007:6: brdas brdas ni dus dang gnad /
NK032(khi)007:8: don spros bral rang rgyud la shar ba'o //
NK032(khi)007:10: pa'i man ngag sbyin ni mi bslu ba'o //
NK032(khi)007:11: bcos med ni ma bcos pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:12: dbyings kyi ni spros pa bral /
NK032(khi)007:17: chos snang stong dbyer med pas /
NK032(khi)007:20: mi snang stong mi 'dzin pa ni nam mkha' lta bu /
NK032(khi)007:22: 'gyur ni snang ba ma 'gags pa sal le sing nge ba de'o //
NK032(khi)007:25: snang ba la der 'dzin 'dzin med pas /
NK032(khi)007:29: dus kyi brda rtsa 'khor lo lnga /
NK032(khi)007:30: la brten rig pa'i rlung tshud pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:32: gnad ni gang 'gyur na nyon mongs pa can gyi yid ni rang rig rang gsal du 'gyur /
NK032(khi)007:33: kyi brda yi gnas gyur pas //
NK032(khi)007:34: gnas yod med rtag chad la sogs su /
NK032(khi)007:36: de la gnyis 'dzin bag chags sogs byed kyi snod ni mi rtog par 'gyur /
NK032(khi)007:37: sa bon cha'i kun gzhi ni chos nyid bde bar 'gyur /
NK032(khi)007:38: rgyu rang las byung ba'i ma rig pa de chos nyid dbyer mi phyed par 'gyur ro //
NK032(khi)007:40: dngos nyi tshe ba'i stong nyid ma yin pas /
NK032(khi)007:41: med kun ldan stong chen po //
NK032(khi)007:42: stong nyid ye shes dag tu bshad //
NK032(khi)007:43: rdo rje zam pa zhes grags yin //
NK032(khi)007:44: na mo gu ru bla ma la phyag 'tshal ba yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)007:45: mchod par brjod skabs sbyor gyi lhan thabs /
NK032(khi)007:47: bstan par dam bca' ba ni chos spyi'i rnam pa ste /
NK032(khi)007:48: don rang gi mtshan nyid kyis gtan la dbab ste /
NK032(khi)007:49: don rang gi mtshan nyid kyis gtan la ma phebs na /
NK032(khi)007:50: gnas lugs kyi don rgyud la mi 'char ro //
NK032(khi)007:51: de la chos spyi'i rnam pa ni /
NK032(khi)007:52: ston pa rnam pa gsum gyis bstan pa'i chos yin te /
NK032(khi)007:53: de la chos kyi sku'i ston pa dpal kun tu bzang pos bstan pa ni /
NK032(khi)007:54: byin gyis brlabs kyis bstan pa'i chos dbang po rab kyi rab /
NK032(khi)007:56: klong sde rab kyi tha ma'i don du 'byung /
NK032(khi)007:58: rgyud dbang po rab kyi chos 'byung tshul /
NK032(khi)007:60: de yang don ched gang la dgongs nas shar /
NK032(khi)007:61: sems gang la dgongs nas shar /
NK032(khi)007:62: de yang sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la sems zhes bya ba gcig yod de /
NK032(khi)007:63: sems de log rtog tu 'dus pas /
NK032(khi)007:64: log par rtog pa de 'dul phyir chos sde shar /
NK032(khi)007:65: sems log rtog de rgyun chad med par 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)007:67: sems log rtog de mi 'dzad par 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)007:69: de bsdu na bslab pa gsum du 'dus /
NK032(khi)007:70: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku'i ston pa dpal rnam par snang mdzad gangs chen mtshos /
NK032(khi)007:71: bstan pa brdas bstan pa'i chos /
NK032(khi)007:72: sku gsung thugs kri ya khyab mi 'gyur ba /
NK032(khi)007:73: yo ga khyab stong pa nyid /
NK032(khi)007:74: u pa khyab ya rnam gang zag 'bring gi tha ma /
NK032(khi)007:78: gang la dgongs nas bstan na /
NK032(khi)007:79: don ched ni sems can thams cad la /
NK032(khi)007:81: lus ngag yid gsum la dgongs nas bstan /
NK032(khi)007:84: yid 'dul phyir u pa ya bstan no //
NK032(khi)007:85: de yang bsdu na bslab pa rnam pa gsum du 'dus /
NK032(khi)007:86: sprul pa'i sku'i ston pa bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pas /
NK032(khi)007:87: bstan pa gang bstan na bstan pa'i chos 'dul ba /
NK032(khi)007:89: mdo sde rnam pa gsum bstan /
NK032(khi)007:90: de yang don ched gang la dgongs nas bshad na /
NK032(khi)007:91: sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la 'dod chags /
NK032(khi)007:93: gti mug la dgongs nas bshad /
NK032(khi)007:94: de yang 'dod chags las gyur pa nyi khri chig stong /
NK032(khi)007:95: zhe sdang las gyur pa nyi khri chig stong /
NK032(khi)007:96: gti mug las gyur pa nyi khrig stong /
NK032(khi)007:97: dug gsum spyi mthun las gyur pa nyi khri chig
NK032(khi)007:98: stong ste nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong du
NK032(khi)007:99: byung ngo // de 'dul ba'i gnyen po ni /
NK032(khi)007:100: gang zag dbang po tha ma'i tha ma'i don du
NK032(khi)007:101: 'dod chags kyi gnyen por 'dul ba nyi khri chig
NK032(khi)007:102: stong gsungs / tha ma'i 'bring gi don du zhe
NK032(khi)007:103: sdang gi gnyen por mdo sde nyi khri chig stong
NK032(khi)007:104: stong gsungs / gsungs / gti tha ma'i rab kyi
NK032(khi)007:105: don du mug gi gnyen por mngon pa nyi khri
NK032(khi)007:106: stong gsungs / gsungs / chig stong gsungs / de
NK032(khi)007:107: yang nyon mongs bsdus pa'i don la dgongs te bka'
NK032(khi)007:108: stong gsungs / gsungs / chig stong gsungs / stsal
NK032(khi)007:109: ba ni / pa bsdus pas rten 'brel bcu gnyis
NK032(khi)007:110: stong gsungs / gsungs / chig stong gsungs / stsal
NK032(khi)007:111: ba ni / su 'dus / dug gsum cha mnyam
NK032(khi)007:112: pa las gyur pa'i gnyen por 'dul ba mdo sde
NK032(khi)007:113: mngon pa gsum spyi dbye ba'i don du dgongs te
NK032(khi)007:114: stong gsungs / gsungs / chig stong gsungs / stsal
NK032(khi)007:115: ba ni / su 'dus / bka' stsal lo //
NK032(khi)007:116: mthun las gyur pa'i nyi khri chig stong gsungs so
NK032(khi)007:117: stong gsungs / gsungs / chig stong gsungs / stsal
NK032(khi)007:118: ba ni / su 'dus / bka' stsal lo //
NK032(khi)007:119: // de las bsdus pas 'dod chags zhe sdang gti
NK032(khi)007:120: mug gsum du 'dus spyi mthun las gyur pa bag
NK032(khi)007:121: stong gsungs / gsungs / chig stong gsungs / stsal
NK032(khi)007:122: ba ni / su 'dus / bka' stsal lo //
NK032(khi)007:123: // la zha / de yang nye bar bsdu na
NK032(khi)007:124: stong gsungs / gsungs / chig stong gsungs / stsal
NK032(khi)007:125: ba ni / su 'dus / bka' stsal lo //
NK032(khi)007:126: // la zha / / dug gsum nyon mongs pa
NK032(khi)007:127: stong gsungs / gsungs / chig stong gsungs / stsal
NK032(khi)007:128: ba ni / su 'dus / bka' stsal lo //
NK032(khi)007:129: // la zha / / can gyi yid / gti
NK032(khi)007:130: stong gsungs / gsungs / chig stong gsungs / stsal
NK032(khi)007:131: ba ni / su 'dus / bka' stsal lo //
NK032(khi)007:132: // la zha / / can gyi yid / mug
NK032(khi)007:133: gi cha / zhe sdang gi cha /
NK032(khi)007:135: ngo bo bag chags sogs pa'i snod /
NK032(khi)007:137: rang bzhin mtshan nyid du gsum du 'dus so //
NK032(khi)007:138: chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis su 'dus /
NK032(khi)007:139: de las nye bar bsdus pas bslab pa rnam pa gsum du 'dus so //
NK032(khi)007:140: de chos spyi'i rnam pa yin te /
NK032(khi)007:141: da don rang gi mtshan nyid du sbyor ba ni /
NK032(khi)007:142: dug gti mug gi cha nyon mongs pa can gyi yid /
NK032(khi)007:143: gsum nye bar bsdus pas ngo bo ma rig pa /
NK032(khi)007:149: mtshan nyid sdug bsngal gsum du 'dus /
NK032(khi)007:150: mdo sde 'dul ba mngon pa gsum nye bar bsdus pas /
NK032(khi)007:151: spros rang gis gsal bde ba /
NK032(khi)007:152: pa med par rtogs pas lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa /
NK032(khi)007:153: de la 'du byed blo yi bye brag gang yang med mi rtog pa /
NK032(khi)007:154: pas lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa /
NK032(khi)007:155: gnas pa med pa'am bral ba yang med de /
NK032(khi)007:156: de bzhin du 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang la mi
NK032(khi)007:157: 'gyur ba de ni lhag pa bsam gtan gyi bslab
NK032(khi)007:158: pa'o / de gsum dbyer mi phyed pa ni chos kyi dbyings so //
NK032(khi)007:159: de yang blo tshig dang bral ba ni chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:160: de yang lung mdo sde nges par 'jog pa las /
NK032(khi)007:161: chos rnams thams cad rgyu las byung //
NK032(khi)007:162: de rgyu de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs //
NK032(khi)007:163: de la 'gog pa gang yin pa //
NK032(khi)007:164: dge sbyong chen pos 'di skad gsungs //
NK032(khi)007:165: sdig ngo bo ma rig pa dag /
NK032(khi)007:166: lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa /
NK032(khi)007:167: pa ci yang mi bya ste //
NK032(khi)007:169: lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa /
NK032(khi)007:170: ba phun sum tshogs par spyad //
NK032(khi)007:171: rang gi sems ni yongs su 'dul lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi bslab pa /
NK032(khi)007:173: 'di ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK032(khi)007:175: chos spyi'i rnam pa de don rang rgyud la sbyar ro //
NK032(khi)007:176: de yang sde snod gsum dang sbyar ba ni /
NK032(khi)007:178: mi rtog pa mdo sde'i sdee snod //
NK032(khi)007:179: gsal ba mngon pa'i sde snod /
NK032(khi)007:180: kri yog gsum dang sbyar ba ni /
NK032(khi)007:181: bde ba kri ya'i sde snod /
NK032(khi)007:182: mi rtog pa u pa ya'i sde snod /
NK032(khi)007:183: gsal pa yo ga'i sde snod /
NK032(khi)007:184: nang pa'i sde snod gsum dang sbyar ba ni /
NK032(khi)007:185: bde ba chos sde'i sde snod /
NK032(khi)007:186: mi rtog pa klong sde'i sde snod /
NK032(khi)007:187: gsal ba rgyud sde'i sde snod /
NK032(khi)007:188: dag tshul rnam pa gsum ni /
NK032(khi)007:189: bde ba lus rnam par dag /
NK032(khi)007:190: gsal ba ngag rnam par dag /
NK032(khi)007:191: mi rtog pa yid rnam par dag pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:194: zhe sdang gnas 'gyur bas mi rtog pa /
NK032(khi)007:195: gti mug gnas 'gyur bas 'od gsal ba'o //
NK032(khi)007:196: skabs sbyor gyi lhan thabs so ////
NK032(khi)007:198: rgya gar rdo rje gdan gyi nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul na /
NK032(khi)007:199: chos skyong ba'i rgyal po d+harma r+aa dza dang /
NK032(khi)007:200: srid skyong ba'i rgyal po u pa r+aa dza zhes pa gnyis yod pa las /
NK032(khi)007:201: chos skyong ba'i rgyal po de chos skyong ba'i gnyer 'ba' zhig ma gtogs pa /
NK032(khi)007:202: srid skyong ba'i gnyer mi byed skad /
NK032(khi)007:203: srid skyong ba'i rgyal po de srid skyong ba'i gnyer 'ba' zhig ma gtogs pa /
NK032(khi)007:204: chos skyong ba'i gnyer mi byed skad /
NK032(khi)007:205: de la chos skyong ba'i rgyal po de la /
NK032(khi)007:206: sras mo lta na phangs pa mdzes pa zhig skyes pas sras mo mdzes dang ldan par btags so //
NK032(khi)007:207: de la lta na phangs zer nas rdzong chen po
NK032(khi)007:208: gcig brtsigs te pho brang bcu gsum gyi rtse la
NK032(khi)007:209: bzhag nas / bskyed bskyed pa de yin /
NK032(khi)007:211: gso ba'i ma mas gsos bas /
NK032(khi)007:212: gzhan gyis lor gsos pa las de'i zla bskyed che /
NK032(khi)007:213: bskyed che legs shes rab che /
NK032(khi)007:214: che ba gcig byung nas yod pa la /
NK032(khi)007:215: dus nam zhig na nam mkha' nas tshur la khu byug gis ltongs ltongs zer ba la /
NK032(khi)007:216: gzhan rnams kyis khu byug rang du go /
NK032(khi)007:218: do nub khyod kyi gan du 'ong ngo bya bar go skad /
NK032(khi)007:219: de nas de'i nub mo srod la khye'u mtshan dang
NK032(khi)007:220: ldan pa gcig nub mo dge ba'i gtam dang sbyor
NK032(khi)007:221: ba byas nas / tu gyur nas byung /
NK032(khi)007:222: nangs par tho rangs khar song skad /
NK032(khi)007:223: de nas sras mo de la zla ba dgu ngo bcu na /
NK032(khi)007:224: bu chung gcig skyes pa las /
NK032(khi)007:225: bskyed che legs che ba gcig byung ba las /
NK032(khi)007:226: lo bdun du mi la gsang nas bsdad /
NK032(khi)007:227: bu de lo brgyad lon tsa na /
NK032(khi)007:228: sras mo mdzes ma dang ldan pas bu de yab rgyal po la gtad pas /
NK032(khi)007:230: e ma ho ngo mtshar che /
NK032(khi)007:231: kyi hud kyi hud zer nas yab rgyal po brgyal lo //
NK032(khi)007:233: sras mos yab rgyal po lags /
NK032(khi)007:234: 'di la pha med pas yab rgyal po ma mnyes lags sam byas pas /
NK032(khi)007:236: 'di la pha med pas 'di rigs byed lha'i sprul pa gcig yin pas /
NK032(khi)007:237: e ma ho ngo mtshar che /
NK032(khi)007:238: 'di'i drin la theg pa chen po'i chos bsam gyis mi khyab pa dar 'ong bar 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)007:239: nga rgas pas kyi hud kyi hud ces nga rang rgas pas mya ngan byas pa yin zer skad /
NK032(khi)007:242: thams cad dga' bas dga' ba'i rab tu gyur pa las /
NK032(khi)007:243: mtshan dga' rab rdo rjer btags so //
NK032(khi)007:244: de nas dga' rab rdo rje'i zhal nas /
NK032(khi)007:245: yum sras mo mdzes ma dang ldan pa khyed 'dir bzhugs shig /
NK032(khi)007:246: nga ni 'di nas nub phyogs su phyin pa na /
NK032(khi)007:247: dpal o rgyan pho skyes thams cad dpa' bo la /
NK032(khi)007:248: mo skyes thams cad mkha' 'gror gyur /
NK032(khi)007:254: thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal lo //
NK032(khi)007:256: d+ha na ko sha'i gling yid pham par byed pa /
NK032(khi)007:257: sems skyo ba skyed par byed pa /
NK032(khi)007:258: phyi'i rgya mtsho ba tsh+wa can no //
NK032(khi)007:260: me tog lo bcu gsum na me tog u dum wa ra re re 'char /
NK032(khi)007:262: me tog de rgya mtsho'i kha chod /
NK032(khi)007:263: me tog sngon po'i 'od nam mkha' la brgyab pas /
NK032(khi)007:265: 'od de ri rab la phog pas ri rab logs gcig mthing gar gyur pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:266: u dum wa ra 'bar ba'i gling /
NK032(khi)007:267: ro mchog dga' ba'i tshal bya ba na dur khrod
NK032(khi)007:268: chen po gser dper na gser gling na rkang stegs
NK032(khi)007:269: sa rdo dang / khyi la brdeg pa'i rdo la
NK032(khi)007:270: sogs pa thams cad gser la spyod pa bzhin du
NK032(khi)007:271: chos nyid rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa la ci skyes
NK032(khi)007:272: pa thams cad chos nyid du longs spyod pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:273: gling he chen brdal chos nyid kyis kun la khyab pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:275: sgrub pa'i gnas skyon dang bral ba /
NK032(khi)007:277: gyi brag don chos nyid mi 'gyur ba /
NK032(khi)007:278: phug yu ba don chos nyid grangs mi chod pas na /
NK032(khi)007:279: yang na grub thob grangs ma chad pas na don chos nyid zab pa /
NK032(khi)007:280: can du 'gro gsung nas der gshegs /
NK032(khi)007:281: de na sgrub pa mdzad pa la /
NK032(khi)007:285: skar ma rgyal gyi nyin par /
NK032(khi)007:286: nangs par nyi ma'i zer la bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa'i sku gsung thugs kyi sprul pa /
NK032(khi)007:287: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' sems dag lha'i bu zhes pa sku mdog dkar po /
NK032(khi)007:288: phyag g.yas na gser gyi rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK032(khi)007:289: g.yon na shel gyi dril bu dku la brten pa /
NK032(khi)007:290: sku la ba ti sngon po gsol ba /
NK032(khi)007:291: zhabs rgyal po rol pa'i stabs kyis bzhugs pa /
NK032(khi)007:292: de snang ba'i gzugs su grub pa la /
NK032(khi)007:293: reg pa'i gzugs su ma grub pa /
NK032(khi)007:294: snang ba'i gzugs su grub pa thabs kyi cha /
NK032(khi)007:295: reg pa'i gzugs su ma grub pa shes rab kyi cha /
NK032(khi)007:296: thabs shes gnyis med kyi tshul du gzigs nas /
NK032(khi)007:297: dga' rab rdo rje'i spyi bor phyag gnyis brkyang nas /
NK032(khi)007:298: a ha ho'i zhes pa'i brda' bstan nas /
NK032(khi)007:299: a ni skye ba med pa /
NK032(khi)007:301: ho ni gnyis su med pa /
NK032(khi)007:302: 'i dbyer mi phyed pa'i don skye 'gag med pa'i thugs su gsal ba lags skad /
NK032(khi)007:305: khyod rang nam mkha' dag par 'ja' shar ba la ltos dang bya bar go skad /
NK032(khi)007:306: 'ja' de snang ba'i gzugs su grub pa thabs kyi
NK032(khi)007:307: cha la reg pa'i gzugs su ma grub pa shes
NK032(khi)007:308: rab kyi cha / thabs shes gnyis su med par thugs su gsal ba lags skad /
NK032(khi)007:309: de lta bu'i chos nyid kyi rang sgra chen po de zhag bdun du byung skad /
NK032(khi)007:310: chos nyid kyi ngang du brgyal ba bya ba lags skad /
NK032(khi)007:313: bdag nyid bee ro tsa na mchis pa 'di //
NK032(khi)007:314: yang dag bcu gcig don dang ye nas ldan //
NK032(khi)007:315: rgya gar yul nas chos bslab nas //
NK032(khi)007:316: sgra don bsdebs nas bka' bsgyur te //
NK032(khi)007:317: bod kyi rgyal khams dkar por btang //
NK032(khi)007:318: rgyal dang blon po kun log nas //
NK032(khi)007:319: spyugs pas tsha ba'i rong du mchis //
NK032(khi)007:320: rgyud sde klong sde'i bka' bkrol nas //
NK032(khi)007:321: g.yu sgra snying po nyid la gtad //
NK032(khi)007:322: tsha ba'i rgyal khams dkar por btang //
NK032(khi)007:323: yang dag don gcig mchis pa de //
NK032(khi)007:324: mi pham mgon po nyid la gtad //
NK032(khi)007:325: skye med nam mkha'i mtha' bzhin rgyas //
NK032(khi)007:326: bdag nyid bee ro tsa na mchis pa 'di //
NK032(khi)007:327: sgyu ma'i phung po bod du smin //
NK032(khi)007:328: sgyu ma'i phung po der smin pas //
NK032(khi)007:329: bdag nyid slar la bod du mchi //
NK032(khi)007:331: phyag rgya mtho do ba mdzad nas /
NK032(khi)007:332: gu na a kar+sha ya zhes lan gsum du gsungs so //
NK032(khi)007:333: sgra dang po'i go ba la /
NK032(khi)007:334: chu bo dag la brten pa'i gru //
NK032(khi)007:335: skya ba drag pos rtsol phod na //
NK032(khi)007:336: grus kyang pha rol phyin par 'gyur //
NK032(khi)007:338: gzhu mo dag la brten pa'i mda' //
NK032(khi)007:339: skyes bu'i mtheb mos rtsol phood na //
NK032(khi)007:340: mdas kyang pha rol phyin par 'gyur //
NK032(khi)007:343: yang dag don la brten pa'i mi //
NK032(khi)007:344: yengs pa med par bsgom nus na //
NK032(khi)007:345: sa phyogs bgrod kyi nyam mi nga //
NK032(khi)007:347: skad cig tsam gyis bsam yas su brtol lo //
NK032(khi)007:348: de nas sngar gyi zhal bzhes lan gcig yar 'ong gsungs pas /
NK032(khi)007:349: des na bsam yas su byon te /
NK032(khi)007:350: sngar chad pa bcad pa'i stobs kyis ming gsang nas phyin /
NK032(khi)007:351: rgyal po dang a ma la sogs pas ngo shes kyang /
NK032(khi)007:352: ngo ma shes pa'i bardzusa btab nas /
NK032(khi)007:353: khyed kyi ming ci yin zer ba la /
NK032(khi)007:354: bee ro tsa nas ming ban chung ye shes sde bya ba yin gsungs so //
NK032(khi)007:355: dus de tsa na sgra bsgyur gyi lo ts+aa ba ska ba dpal brtsegs /
NK032(khi)007:356: sgra phran bu bsgyur ba'i lo ts+aa ba cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan /
NK032(khi)007:357: ka kha gug bskyed la sogs pa bsgyur ba'i lo
NK032(khi)007:358: ts+aa ba legs spong rgyal ba'i byang chub la sogs
NK032(khi)007:359: pa lo ts+aa ba bzhi sgroms su bcug nas 'dug
NK032(khi)007:360: pa la / don bsgyur ba'i lo ts+aa ba gcig kyang mi 'dug nas /
NK032(khi)007:361: ban+de ye shes sde khyed kyis don bsgyur shes sam byas pa las /
NK032(khi)007:362: ngas sgra rigs mi 'dra ba bar 'dir ma phyir
NK032(khi)007:363: ldeb gcig chad song 'dug pa slar rnyed na 'dzud
NK032(khi)007:364: mdzod / mi gnas pa'i stong pa dang /
NK032(khi)007:365: sngags la lhag par mos pa'i ston pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:367: rdo rje gzegs mas gzhig pa dang /
NK032(khi)007:368: gcig dang du bral gyis gzhig pa'i stong pa dang /
NK032(khi)007:369: mu bzhi skye 'gog gis gzhig pa dang /
NK032(khi)007:372: rdza'i 'jim pa'i gong bu la ming dang bya ba ma grub pa lta bu'o //
NK032(khi)007:374: stong pa res 'jog can lta bu'o //
NK032(khi)007:376: dngos po snga ma gzhig nas phyi ma bsgom pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:377: de rnams la ni sems can blo'i stong pa zhes bya ste /
NK032(khi)007:378: chos spyi'i rnam par shor nas snang ba gtan la phab pas 'khor ba las mi grol lo //
NK032(khi)007:379: rnal 'byor pa lam gyi stong pa ni /
NK032(khi)007:380: rgya gar gyi yul byang phyogs sing+ga la na /
NK032(khi)007:381: de'i nang dur khrod chen po so sa'i gling bya ba yod /
NK032(khi)007:382: de nas rnam 'byor pa da na d+ha bya bas
NK032(khi)007:383: sna drangs pa'i rnal 'byor pa brgya nyag gcig gnas
NK032(khi)007:384: pa las / dus nam zhig na rigs byed 'khyams po ba gcig byung nas /
NK032(khi)007:385: khyod rnal 'byor pa da na d+ha yin nam zer /
NK032(khi)007:387: 'o na nga'i lus 'di khyod la 'bul lo //
NK032(khi)007:388: rme ba bdun yod kyis zer /
NK032(khi)007:389: 'o na khyod kyi lus de nged la phul nas /
NK032(khi)007:392: der kho hrul gyis shi nas bshas pas /
NK032(khi)007:393: go ro tsa na bya ba klad pa bre gang byung skad /
NK032(khi)007:394: rak+ta bya ba khrag bre gang byung skad /
NK032(khi)007:395: ba su ta bya ba rgyu ma nang der 'o mar gyur pa bre gang byung skad /
NK032(khi)007:396: de tsho snod gcig tu blugs nas bkrogs pas /
NK032(khi)007:397: mar du gyur pa byung skad /
NK032(khi)007:398: de rnal 'byor pa brgya nyag gcig la thur ma re re drangs nas gsol bas /
NK032(khi)007:399: chos nyid kyi don rgyud la skyes skad /
NK032(khi)007:400: de nas lhag ma rnams kyang rim pas gsol lo //
NK032(khi)007:401: der rnal 'byor pa da na d+has spyan 'og tu gzigs pas /
NK032(khi)007:403: rigs byed pa 'di ci yang ma yin pa gcig yin zer ro //
NK032(khi)007:404: de lung gang gis shes nas /
NK032(khi)007:408: nam mkha' ci la yang rten mi 'cha' ba yin zer bas shes /
NK032(khi)007:409: yang pra dz+ny+aa pa ra las /
NK032(khi)007:410: sems la sgrib pa med pas skrag pa med /
NK032(khi)007:412: de la go lugs rnam pa gsum byung ste /
NK032(khi)007:413: sgra drang thad du go byar med bzhag chog tu go ba yin te /
NK032(khi)007:414: las dge ba bsags rgyu med /
NK032(khi)007:418: sgra lhun grub tu go ni lhun grub chen po
NK032(khi)007:419: gsal ba la stong pa'i rgyas thebs pas stong pa'i
NK032(khi)007:421: de ma yengs yongs su rdzogs pa'i go ba'o //
NK032(khi)007:423: sgra thang log tu go ba ni bsad pa gso bar nus pa /
NK032(khi)007:424: mi dad pa dad par nus pa /
NK032(khi)007:425: de ltar bskyur ba na thang log tu go ba'o //
NK032(khi)007:430: nam mkha' ci la yang rten mi 'cha' zhes sngar lung gi don ltar zer skad /
NK032(khi)007:431: gcig dang du bral gyis chos thams cad rang bzhin med par gtan la dbab pa ni gnyis las /
NK032(khi)007:433: med bzhin du snang ba'i 'khrul pa de sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad dang mtshungs so //
NK032(khi)007:436: da ltar gyi shes pa skyes la ma 'gags pa tsam yang ma grub ste /
NK032(khi)007:437: spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'o //
NK032(khi)007:438: de yang slob dpon klu sgrub kyi zhal nas /
NK032(khi)007:441: yod med mu bzhi skye 'gog gi mtha' bzhi'i spros pa bcad pa ni /
NK032(khi)007:443: sna tshogs rtag pa ma yin te //
NK032(khi)007:444: chad par yang ni khas mi len //
NK032(khi)007:445: rtag dang chad dang gnyis ka dang //
NK032(khi)007:446: gnyis ka min pa'ang ma yin no //
NK032(khi)007:447: mdor na thams cad mi gnas par //
NK032(khi)007:448: dngos po de nyid mkhas pas rig /
NK032(khi)007:449: des na 'di lta'i rnam dag go //
NK032(khi)007:450: sems ni sems kyis rig ma yin //
NK032(khi)007:451: ji srid sgro 'dogs thams cad ni //
NK032(khi)007:452: de srid thams cad du med pas //
NK032(khi)007:453: dbu ma'i don la sgro 'dogs med //
NK032(khi)007:454: des na bdag tu grub pa med //
NK032(khi)007:457: 'di la bsal bya ci yang med //
NK032(khi)007:458: bzhag par bya ba gang yang med //
NK032(khi)007:459: yang dag nyid la yang dag lta //
NK032(khi)007:460: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK032(khi)007:461: zhes pas yod pa'i sgro 'dogs dang /
NK032(khi)007:462: med pa'i skur pa 'debs pa la mi gnas pa de /
NK032(khi)007:463: sems nyid sna tshogs su snang ba /
NK032(khi)007:464: nyams su myong ba de nyid rten cing 'brel te 'byung bas na ma skyes te /
NK032(khi)007:465: ma skyes pa nyid skye ba ltar snang ste /
NK032(khi)007:466: ma skyes pa dang skye ba gnyis tha mi dad pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:467: de bzhin du snang ba 'di rig pas brtags na stong pa yin la /
NK032(khi)007:468: stong pa ma grub pa'i rig pas brtag mi bzod pa nyid snang ba'o //
NK032(khi)007:469: snang ba nyid las kyang stong pa gzhan ma yin /
NK032(khi)007:470: stong pa las kyang snang ba gzhan ma yin no //
NK032(khi)007:471: dper na smig sgyu la chur snang ba nyid las chu med de /
NK032(khi)007:472: chu stong la chu med pa nyid du chur snang ngo //
NK032(khi)007:473: chur snang ba dang chu med pa tha dad pa ma yin no //
NK032(khi)007:474: de bzhin du snang ba rang bzhin med la /
NK032(khi)007:475: rang bzhin med pa nyid snang ba'o //
NK032(khi)007:476: snang ba dang rang bzhin med pa'i stong pa nyid tha mi dad do //
NK032(khi)007:478: shing dum mes bsreg na me'i ngo bo gcig ste /
NK032(khi)007:479: de nas bud shing zad pa dang /
NK032(khi)007:481: de bzhin du sna tshogs su snang ba nyid rig
NK032(khi)007:482: pas stong pa nyid du byas nas dngos po ma
NK032(khi)007:483: grub pa dang / stong pa nyid kyang mi gnas so //
NK032(khi)007:484: de bzhin du gnyis su med pa yang gnyis su
NK032(khi)007:485: ma grub pa'i tshe na gnyis su med pa yang
NK032(khi)007:486: mi grub pa'o // de bas na gzhan gyi zhen pa bzlog pa'am /
NK032(khi)007:488: drang ba'i don du stong pa nyid dang /
NK032(khi)007:490: gnyis su med pa zhes brjod kyis mkhas pas btsal ba'am /
NK032(khi)007:491: dngos po'i don du de nyid mi gnas te /
NK032(khi)007:495: skur 'debs gang du yang mi gnas la /
NK032(khi)007:496: zhen pa med cing dgag pa dang /
NK032(khi)007:498: mnyam bzhag dang rjes thob gnyis su med cing mi gnas pa ni lta ba'o //
NK032(khi)007:499: rdo rje gzegs mas skye med sems la ngo sprad pa ni /
NK032(khi)007:501: bdag las ma yin gzhan las min //
NK032(khi)007:502: gnyis las ma yin rgyu med min //
NK032(khi)007:503: dngos po gang dang gang la yang //
NK032(khi)007:504: skye ba nam yang yod ma yin //
NK032(khi)007:506: bdag ma grub pa'i rgyu mtshan gsum ste /
NK032(khi)007:507: ming gloo bur du btags pas bdag ma yin te /
NK032(khi)007:514: lus 'byung ba chen po bzhi la brten nas 'byung ba yin pas bdag ma yin /
NK032(khi)007:515: sems ni snang du rung ba las ma dmigs pa'i phyir /
NK032(khi)007:516: rang gis kyang ma mthong gzhan gyis kyang ma mthong bas bdag ma yin te /
NK032(khi)007:518: sems ni 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang ma gzigs mi gzigs gzigs par mi 'gyur ro //
NK032(khi)007:519: ma byon pa dang da lta la yang sbyar ro //
NK032(khi)007:520: yang rang gis mthong na yul du byas nas mthong ngam ma byas kyang mthong /
NK032(khi)007:521: byas nas mthong na yul dang yul can gnyis su 'gyur /
NK032(khi)007:522: yul du ma byas kyang mthong na /
NK032(khi)007:524: gzhan gyis mthong na gzhan rig tu 'gyur /
NK032(khi)007:526: de la mthong byed gzhan yod pas thug med du thal ba'i skyon 'ong /
NK032(khi)007:527: de ltar bdag ma grub tsa na /
NK032(khi)007:528: de la ltos pa'i bdag gir yang ma grub bo //
NK032(khi)007:529: rten cing 'brel 'byung gis rtag chad kyi log lta bsal ba ni /
NK032(khi)007:530: sa lu ljang pa'i mdo las /
NK032(khi)007:534: sa bon las myu gu 'byung ba yin te /
NK032(khi)007:535: myu gu las kyang sdong bu dang /
NK032(khi)007:537: nas kyi bar du skye la /
NK032(khi)007:538: sa bon de la sna tshogs skye ba'i rgyu du ma /
NK032(khi)007:539: yod bzhin du mi mthong la /
NK032(khi)007:540: rten 'brel tshogs pa'i dus su du ma skyes kyang sa bon de myu gur 'ong ba med la /
NK032(khi)007:541: sa bon la ma brten par myu gu 'byung ba med do //
NK032(khi)007:542: de bzhin du rang gi sems la dge sdig gi las sna tshogs kyi bag chags la brten nas /
NK032(khi)007:543: rigs drug tu bde sdug sna tshogs skye ba'i rgyur gnas kyang da lta mi mthong la /
NK032(khi)007:544: rkyen tshogs nas shi nas skye ba'i tshe sna tshogs
NK032(khi)007:545: snang yang tshe 'dir snang ba'i shes pa phyi mar
NK032(khi)007:547: tshe 'di'i rnam par shes pa la ma brten par phyi ma 'byung ba yang med do //
NK032(khi)007:548: 'di ma rtogs pa rnams la rtag par lta ba'i blo skye'o //
NK032(khi)007:549: snga ma phyi mar 'ong ba med pas skye ba med pa zhes bya ba yin te /
NK032(khi)007:550: 'di ma rtogs pa rnams chad par lta ba'i blo skye'o //
NK032(khi)007:558: dbus med pas chos thams cad la sgro 'dogs skur
NK032(khi)007:559: pa 'debs pa las yongs su grol ba ni rten
NK032(khi)007:560: cing 'brel bar 'byung ba zhes bya ba yin no
NK032(khi)007:563: bka' rdzogs pa chen po bka' babs phyi ma'i bka'
NK032(khi)007:564: sa man+ta bde ba kun spyod kyi lam gtan la
NK032(khi)007:565: dbab pa dang / nyams su blang ba'o //
NK032(khi)007:566: de la rdo rje snying po don gtan la 'bebs pa'i rgyud sde bcu gsum las /
NK032(khi)007:567: rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba /
NK032(khi)007:568: bshad pa'i rgyud badz+ra sa man+ta nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud /
NK032(khi)007:569: sgom pa'i rgyud ye shes rdzogs pa /
NK032(khi)007:570: dka' ba gcod pa klong dgu'i rgyud dang /
NK032(khi)007:574: spyod pa bsdus pa rgya mtsho sgron ma'i rgyud yang snang /
NK032(khi)007:575: e a ral+li rnyogs pa med pa'i rgyud /
NK032(khi)007:577: rig pa nam mkha' ltar gsal ba'i rgyud /
NK032(khi)007:579: bka' sa man+ta phyi ma'i phyi ma 'od kyi rgyud /
NK032(khi)007:581: pad+ma'i snying po'i don nyams su blang ba'i sgrub sde bcu gsum las /
NK032(khi)007:582: de dag gi man ngag rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa dang dbang gi man ngag1 /
NK032(khi)007:583: zam pa chen po 'phrul gyi me long brtsegs pa chen po dang 2 /
NK032(khi)007:593: de dag gi don bsdus pa rna brgyud gser lung yang snang /
NK032(khi)007:595: theg pa thams cad kyi don bsdus pa rin po che me gser rdzong yang snang /
NK032(khi)007:596: rin chen gser phreng yin par 'dug /
NK032(khi)007:598: de la rgyud sde bcu gsum gyi don /
NK032(khi)007:599: sgrub sde bcu gsum gyi snying po /
NK032(khi)007:600: rna brgyud rin po che rdo rje zam pa /
NK032(khi)007:601: bden chen zag med kyi skad 'di lags so //
NK032(khi)007:605: grol ba mthar phyin pa rdo rje'i tshig ni /
NK032(khi)007:607: sems kyi mtshan nyid stong pa ci yang ma yin pa de'o //
NK032(khi)007:609: bsgom rgyu med kyang don gyi gzer chen 'debs dgos /
NK032(khi)007:610: sgom med don gyi gzer chen gdab pa la /
NK032(khi)007:612: go ba ni sems yid yul lam bsam yul la mi gnas pas sgom du med /
NK032(khi)007:613: gzer ces pa'i go ba ni /
NK032(khi)007:614: sems nyid ci yang ma yin pa de brda' dang ngag gis bstan pas /
NK032(khi)007:615: de mthong nas ngo shes pa de ni /
NK032(khi)007:616: mi 'chug mi 'gyur ba de gzer ces bya'o //
NK032(khi)007:618: gnad kyi brda' dang dus kyi barda'o //
NK032(khi)007:619: dus kyi brda' snying po ye shes kyi rlung /
NK032(khi)007:620: a wa d+hu tir tshud pa de'o //
NK032(khi)007:621: a wa d+hu ti ni lnga ste /
NK032(khi)007:622: spyi bo gtsug tor gyi a wa d+hu ti dang /
NK032(khi)007:623: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi a wa d+hu ti dang /
NK032(khi)007:624: snying kha shes rab kyi a wa d+hu ti dang /
NK032(khi)007:625: lte ba sprul pa'i a wa d+hu ti dang /
NK032(khi)007:626: gsang ba bde ba bskyed pa'i a wa d+hu ti dang lnga'o //
NK032(khi)007:630: kun 'dar ma spyi bo nas gsang bar thig gdab pa lta bur gnas /
NK032(khi)007:631: spyi bor rtsa kun 'dar ma la rtsa ro mas g.yas nas g.yon du 'khyud /
NK032(khi)007:633: kun 'dar ma la rkyang mas g.yon nas g.yas su 'khyud /
NK032(khi)007:635: de gsum spyi bor gcig tu 'dzom pa de las
NK032(khi)007:636: spyi bo'i gtsug tor gyi a wa d+hu ti zer
NK032(khi)007:638: snying po ye shes kyi rlung a wa d+hu ti gang la tshud kyang g.yon nas 'gyu /
NK032(khi)007:639: 'gyu ba'i dus kyi brda' yin pas /
NK032(khi)007:640: sems nyid ci yang ma yin par gnas te de'i dus su tha mal la yengs par 'ong ngo //
NK032(khi)007:641: de ngo ma shes na bag la nyal yin de'i
NK032(khi)007:642: dus su gnad kyi brda' bzhi rgyud la sbyar nas
NK032(khi)007:643: / dus kyi brda' de gnas bsgyur ba yin /
NK032(khi)007:644: bag la nyal de ngo shes na chos nyid skur shar bas der gnas bsgyur ba yin /
NK032(khi)007:647: rang gi rig pa tshad ma /
NK032(khi)007:648: rgyud dang mi 'gal ba'i tshad ma /
NK032(khi)007:649: tshad ma bzhi'i skya bar du bcug nas mi 'gal bar bstan te /
NK032(khi)007:650: gsang sngags thams cad kyi rtsa rgyud m+au la tan+t+ra'i rtsa ba nas /
NK032(khi)007:651: ci yang ma yin gnas 'gyur bas //
NK032(khi)007:654: rna brgyud lung gi phreng ba las /
NK032(khi)007:655: dus kyi brda' la brten nas kyang //
NK032(khi)007:656: sdug bsngal chu bo che las sgrol //
NK032(khi)007:658: slob dpon rba sgom gyi zhal nas /
NK032(khi)007:659: dus kyi brda' la brten nas kyang //
NK032(khi)007:660: gnad kyi brda' yis gnas 'gyur te //
NK032(khi)007:664: sems la sgrib pa med cing skrag pa med de
NK032(khi)007:665: phyin ci log las shin tu 'das nas mya ngan
NK032(khi)007:668: de ltar ci yang ma yin pa'i sems nyid de gnas 'gyur /
NK032(khi)007:669: rang gi rig pa ni rdos khab blangs pa bzhin
NK032(khi)007:670: du rang gi rgyud la tsen gyis lon pa de
NK032(khi)007:672: dper na zangs lcags la gser 'gyur gyi rtsi btang ba ltar ro //
NK032(khi)007:674: rdzas kyis lung ni gnas 'gyur ba //
NK032(khi)007:675: phying ba spyi rings kyi 'od khang la //
NK032(khi)007:676: nang du klad pa'i gur phub la //
NK032(khi)007:677: shug tshil lam gu gul phugs su byug /
NK032(khi)007:678: zhun chen gyi mar me nang du btang //
NK032(khi)007:679: me lce dang dud pas phugs su bdug /
NK032(khi)007:680: de ltar byas pa'i shug tshil lam //
NK032(khi)007:681: gu gul gnyis kyi dud pa yis //
NK032(khi)007:682: shangs bug g.yas nas bdug par bya //
NK032(khi)007:683: des ni g.yon du 'gyur ba yin //
NK032(khi)007:684: rlung gnas 'gyur ba dus kyi brda' //
NK032(khi)007:685: de dus gnad kyi brda' yis blta //
NK032(khi)007:686: nyams su myong bar the tshom med //
NK032(khi)007:687: gnad gcod kyi na tsha zhi bar nus //
NK032(khi)007:688: bde ba 'char bar the tshom med //
NK032(khi)007:689: des na rdzas 'di brten pa gces //
NK032(khi)007:690: rje rgyal ba 'dzeng gi zhal gdams so //
NK032(khi)007:692: slob dpon bee ro tsa na nas snying po bcu gsum gyi mgur bzhengs ba /
NK032(khi)007:693: pha yi snying po kun tu bzang po lur //
NK032(khi)007:694: ma yi snying po kun tu bzang mo mchod //
NK032(khi)007:695: chung ma'i snying po chos nyid bag mar longs //
NK032(khi)007:696: sras kyi snying po bde gshegs rigs lnga bskyed //
NK032(khi)007:697: man ngag snying po bla ma slob dpon tshol //
NK032(khi)007:698: zas kyi snying po bla ma'i man ngag gsol //
NK032(khi)007:699: grol gyi snying po rgyal ba'i bka' la dris //
NK032(khi)007:700: mtshon gyi snying po shes rab ral gri thogs //
NK032(khi)007:701: mthu yi snying po rang gi dug lnga brubs //
NK032(khi)007:702: mgyogs pa'i snying po brtson 'grus rta la zhon //
NK032(khi)007:703: grogs kyi snying po mnyam nyid don dang 'grogs //
NK032(khi)007:704: ltad mo'i snying po rang gi sems la ltos //
NK032(khi)007:705: skom gyi snying po bdud rtsi nying khu 'thung //
NK032(khi)007:706: snying po bcu gsum gyi mgur +thii //
NK032(khi)007:707: slob dpon bee ro tsa na nas rgyal mo tsha ba'i rong du mgur bzhengs pa /
NK032(khi)007:708: skye 'chi med pa'i don rtogs na //
NK032(khi)007:709: chos sku thob rung ma thob rung //
NK032(khi)007:710: lta rgyu med pa'i don rtogs na //
NK032(khi)007:711: lta ba mkhas rung mi mkhas rung //
NK032(khi)007:712: the tshom med pa'i don rtogs na //
NK032(khi)007:714: dngos gzhi med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK032(khi)007:715: 'bras bu thob rung mi thob rung //
NK032(khi)007:716: bgrod du med pa'i don rtogs na //
NK032(khi)007:717: gnas kun mtho rung mi mtho rung //
NK032(khi)007:718: rang byung ye shes don rtogs na //
NK032(khi)007:719: 'dus byas rtag rung mi rtag rung //
NK032(khi)007:720: rtog med mnyam med don rtogs na //
NK032(khi)007:721: bag chags sogs rung mi sogs rung //
NK032(khi)007:722: brjod du med pa'i don rtogs na //
NK032(khi)007:723: tha snyad mkhas rung mi mkhas rung //
NK032(khi)007:724: dmigs su med pa'i don rtogs na //
NK032(khi)007:725: mnyam par bzhag rung ma bzhag rung //
NK032(khi)007:726: bcos su med pa'i don rtogs na //
NK032(khi)007:727: rnam rtog byung rung ma byung rung //
NK032(khi)007:728: gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs na //
NK032(khi)007:729: theg pa bgrang rung ma bgrang rung //

NK032(khi)007:736: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes mgur bzhengs pa /
NK032(khi)007:738: yul rnams thams cad blta 'dod na //

NK032(khi)007:740: chos rnams skye 'gags med pa'i yul //
NK032(khi)007:741: rang sems rig na ri rab rtse //
NK032(khi)007:743: rgya mtsho chen po'i chu la 'thung //
NK032(khi)007:744: skye med byang chub sems kyi chu //

NK032(khi)007:749: byang chub sems kyi me chen spor //

NK032(khi)007:753: byang sems dgon pa'i gnas 'di che //

NK032(khi)007:756: byang chub sems ni rin po che //

NK032(khi)007:763: chu bo bzhin du rgyun chad med //
NK032(khi)007:764: byang chub sems ni rin po che //
NK032(khi)007:765: 'ja' tshon bzhin du bzung du med //
NK032(khi)007:766: byang chub sems ni rin po che //

NK032(khi)007:773: stag gi lo dpyid zla ra ba'i tshes bcu gsum /
NK032(khi)007:775: skar ma rgyal gyi nub mo /
NK032(khi)007:776: +aar+ya pa lo'i gling du bsogs nas /
NK032(khi)007:777: der gzims pas gung gcig la rmi lam bzhi byung /
NK032(khi)007:778: srod la thun gcig nyal ba'i rmi lam na //
NK032(khi)007:779: bud med lo brgyad lon pa gzhon nu mas //
NK032(khi)007:781: bdag gi phung po'i khog pa kha phyes nas //
NK032(khi)007:782: bdag gi snying phyungs chu ser 'dzag pa rmis //
NK032(khi)007:783: dgung la thun gcig log pa'i rmi lam na //
NK032(khi)007:784: rgya gar skyes bu nyi shu rtsa gcig gi snying phyungs nas //
NK032(khi)007:785: snying nyi shu rtsa gcig zos pa rmis //
NK032(khi)007:786: tho rangs thun gcig log pa'i rmi lam na //
NK032(khi)007:787: rgya gar yul gyi mi rengs skya bo gcig gis ni //
NK032(khi)007:788: bee ro tsa na'i spyir bor yi ge ahbazhaga ste /
NK032(khi)007:789: ahls me 'bar gzugs phung bsregs pa rmis //
NK032(khi)007:790: nam langs khar thun gcig log pa'i rmi lam na //
NK032(khi)007:791: rgya gar yul gyi byang chub shing drung de //
NK032(khi)007:792: rtsa ba nas bcad de bod la khur ba rmis //
NK032(khi)007:793: de nas gtsang legs grub la rmi ltas bshad pa /
NK032(khi)007:794: grogs po skyid do yar bzhengs dang //
NK032(khi)007:795: rmi lam bzang po thang bzhi bdag la rmis //
NK032(khi)007:796: srod la thun gcig log pa'i rmi lam na //
NK032(khi)007:797: bud med lo brgyad lon pa'i gzhon sha can //
NK032(khi)007:798: ye shes ral gri 'od du 'bar ba yis //
NK032(khi)007:799: bdag gi phung po'i khog pa kha phyes nas //
NK032(khi)007:800: don snying rnam lnga 'don pa rmis //
NK032(khi)007:801: chu ser 'dzag cing rmi ba de //
NK032(khi)007:802: sngon gyi bag chags rnam byang nas //
NK032(khi)007:803: las ngan sgrib pa dag pa'i rtags //
NK032(khi)007:804: rmi lam bzang ngo 'o skol myur du gshegs //
NK032(khi)007:805: dgung la thun gcig nyal ba'i rmi lam na //
NK032(khi)007:806: rgya gar skyes pa nyi shu rtsa gcig gi //
NK032(khi)007:807: snying phyung tsit+ta nyi shu rtsa gcig rnams //
NK032(khi)007:808: bee ro tsa na bdag gis zos rmis te //
NK032(khi)007:809: gung sngon gyi bag chags rmis pa ste //
NK032(khi)007:810: sngon gyi las 'phro skal bar ldan pa yis //
NK032(khi)007:811: rgya gar yul gyi mkhas pa'i man ngag bde chen rnams //
NK032(khi)007:812: bee ro tsa na bdag gis thon pa'i rtags //
NK032(khi)007:813: rmi lam bzang bas 'o skol myur du gshegs //
NK032(khi)007:814: tho rangs thun gcig log pa'i rmi lam na //
NK032(khi)007:815: rgya gar yul gyi mi rengs skya bo gcig gis ni //
NK032(khi)007:816: bdag gi spyi bo'i gtsug tu a bzhag ste //
NK032(khi)007:817: a las ye shes me 'bar nas //
NK032(khi)007:818: gzugs kyi phung po bsregs pa'i snang ba rmis //
NK032(khi)007:819: a ni chos sku skye med dag pa'i rtags //
NK032(khi)007:820: skye med ye shes 'bar ba yis //
NK032(khi)007:821: bdag gi gzugs kyi phung po yi //
NK032(khi)007:822: nyon mongs bag chags bsregs pa'i rtags //
NK032(khi)007:823: rmi lam bzang bas 'o skol myur du gshegs //
NK032(khi)007:824: nam langs khar thun gcig log pa'i rmi lam na //
NK032(khi)007:825: rgya gar yul gyi byang chub shing drung de //
NK032(khi)007:826: rtsad nas bcad de bod du khur ba rmis //
NK032(khi)007:827: bee ro tsa na bdag gis ni //
NK032(khi)007:828: gdams ngag ma lus thob pa'i rtags //
NK032(khi)007:829: rmi lam bzang bas 'o skol myur du gshegs //
NK032(khi)007:830: de skad gsungs nas rgya gar yul du gshegs so //
NK032(khi)007:831: bee ro tsa nas rmi lam brtag pa bzang ngo //
NK032(khi)007:832: o rgyan yul gyi mtshan nyid ni //
NK032(khi)007:833: o rgyan mthil ni sla nga 'dra //
NK032(khi)007:834: o rgyan yul ni dbyar dgun med //
NK032(khi)007:835: o rgyan yul ni me tog rnam par mang po 'khrungs //
NK032(khi)007:836: o rgyan yul ni za 'og snam bur 'dra //
NK032(khi)007:837: o rgyan yul ni gangs ri gangs kyis bskor //
NK032(khi)007:838: gangs dang nags kyi mtshams na nags tshal 'thug pos bltams //
NK032(khi)007:839: mtha' bzhi bar mtshams na gangs kyis bskor //
NK032(khi)007:840: o rgyan yul du 'khrungs pa'i skal ldan rnams ston dpyid so nams bya mi dgos /
NK032(khi)007:842: 'dzam bu bri shar ro mchog brgya dang ldan //
NK032(khi)007:843: mo btsun bal thag bya mi dgos //
NK032(khi)007:844: 'dzam bu bri sha lpags pa dar las 'jam //
NK032(khi)007:845: byis pa rnams la rnam rtog gdod nas dag nas med //
NK032(khi)007:846: pha dang ma ru mi slob dgra dang gnyen gyi ming yang med //
NK032(khi)007:847: tsha dang zhang du mi slob grogs po'i ming yang med //
NK032(khi)007:848: bden rdzun gnyis su mi slob blo yi yul las 'das //
NK032(khi)007:850: de ru 'khrungs pa'i yon tan gyis //
NK032(khi)007:851: mkha' 'gro rnam bzhi'i sku yang dngos su ston //
NK032(khi)007:852: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin rnams kyang de na bzhugs //
NK032(khi)007:853: rdo rje sems dpa'i sku yang dngos su ston //
NK032(khi)007:854: ha cang mi dro ha cang mi grang ste //
NK032(khi)007:855: 'dod yon lnga la longs spyod khyad par can du gnas //
NK032(khi)007:856: tshe la bar chad mi 'ong rang re gang dgar sdod //
NK032(khi)007:857: o rgyan yul gyi 'phrang rnams brag gis bskor //
NK032(khi)007:858: brag 'phrang la zla ba gcig tu gnas //
NK032(khi)007:859: de nas chu la zla ba gsum yod //
NK032(khi)007:860: de nas ri med brag med nags med thang gcig yod //
NK032(khi)007:861: de nas nyi ma gcig gis sleb //
NK032(khi)007:862: yang na byang chub sems dpa'i sa'am /
NK032(khi)007:863: grub pa thob pa ma lags pa'i gang zag phal pa lam la thar sa med /
NK032(khi)007:864: gcan gzan gdug pa can dang dred kyi tshogs //
NK032(khi)007:866: ha la 'bar byed kyi tshogs dang chu'i lam dang brag lam la thar srid kyang /
NK032(khi)007:867: ha la gdug pa'i tshogs las thar sa med do //
NK032(khi)007:868: o rgyan yul gyi rnam thar +thii /
NK032(khi)007:869: skabs sbyor lhan thabs rgyas pa /
NK032(khi)007:870: ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK032(khi)007:871: gdod nas dag pa'i byang chub sems nyid kyis //
NK032(khi)007:872: nyid kyi ngo bo nyid kyi don bstan pa //
NK032(khi)007:873: zhes bya ba sngon du mchod par brjod cing /
NK032(khi)007:874: bstan par dam bca' ba ston pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:875: spyir gdams ngag gi lugs kyis mchod par brjod pa mi 'byung ba lags /
NK032(khi)007:878: gdams ngag la mi 'byung ba rgyu mtshan de'i lugs kyi rang gi rgyud la nyams su myong tshod /
NK032(khi)007:881: rgyud kyi don gyi'agro tshod dam /
NK032(khi)007:882: don mi bslu ba'i man ngag nyung la 'dus pa de bla mas gdams ngag tu ston pa las /
NK032(khi)007:885: mjug yongs su bsdu ba la sogs pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK032(khi)007:886: rgyud la sogs ba la 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK032(khi)007:889: mjug yongs su bsdu ba la sogs pa yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK032(khi)007:891: yul gang la mchod par brjod na /
NK032(khi)007:893: sgrub thabs kyi gtso bo'i lha'am /
NK032(khi)007:894: bstan bcos rtsom pa po'i yi dam lha la sogs pa la mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:895: de yang 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lugs kyi he ru ka'am /
NK032(khi)007:898: rdo rje sems dpa' la gtso cher brjod do //
NK032(khi)007:899: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi lugs kyis yum chen mo'am /
NK032(khi)007:900: bstan pa'i bdag po la gtso cher brjod do //
NK032(khi)007:901: gdams ngag la rgya la byung na'ang brgyud pa'i bla ma la mchod pa yin te /
NK032(khi)007:902: de'ang yul gzhan la mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:903: gdams ngag 'di'i lugs la mchod brjod 'byung ba'o //
NK032(khi)007:904: de'i rgyu mtshan gang zag gis go tshod /
NK032(khi)007:906: blo'i bcos ma lta bu gcig ma yin te /
NK032(khi)007:907: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa gcig nas gcig tu brjod pas dgongs don gyi brgyud pa'am /
NK032(khi)007:908: rgyud kyi don man ngag tu bstan pas na rgyud dang 'dra ba'i gdams ngag /
NK032(khi)007:909: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sprul pa sems dag lha'i bu nas /
NK032(khi)007:910: da lta yan chad bka' brgyud phreng ba ma chad
NK032(khi)007:911: pas na rgyud dang 'dra ba'i gdams ngag gcig 'di
NK032(khi)007:913: de'ang yul pha rol gzhan la ma yin te /
NK032(khi)007:914: nyid la nyid mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:915: tshul ji ltar na rang gi sems nyid brjod du
NK032(khi)007:916: med pa'i ngang de la phyag 'tshal ba'i tshul ston
NK032(khi)007:917: pa'o // rang la rang gi phyag 'tshal ba de cang 'thad dam zhe na /
NK032(khi)007:919: sems las sangs rgyas med pas mchod pa gzhan mi bya //
NK032(khi)007:920: re dogs gnyis su med pas smon lam gzhan mi gdab //
NK032(khi)007:922: kun tu bzang po che ba rang la gnas pa'i rgyud las /
NK032(khi)007:923: chos kyi dbyings na gcig pur bzhugs pa'i lha //
NK032(khi)007:924: don dam byang chub sems kyi lha yin te //
NK032(khi)007:925: don dam sems kyi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK032(khi)007:927: rdo rje zam pa'i rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)007:928: yon tan thams cad ma btsal rang la shar //
NK032(khi)007:929: rtogs pa'i rim pas gnyis med ngang la 'dud //
NK032(khi)007:931: de bas nyid la nyid phyag 'tshal ba la 'gal ba med do //
NK032(khi)007:933: ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK032(khi)007:935: de la dang po ma nor zhes pa ni /
NK032(khi)007:936: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid kyi don /
NK032(khi)007:937: sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs rang byung
NK032(khi)007:938: gi ye shes chen po de dus gsum du 'du
NK032(khi)007:941: skye 'gag med pa'i chos bzhi dang ldan pa'i don
NK032(khi)007:942: 'dus ma byas pa'i dbyings 'gyur ba med pa de
NK032(khi)007:943: gsal la rtogs pa med pa nam mkha'i dkyil lta
NK032(khi)007:944: bu / phyin ci ma log par rtogs pas na ma nor ba'o //
NK032(khi)007:945: ma nor ba'i don de nyid la sangs rgyas sgam ste mdzad du ma btub /
NK032(khi)007:946: sems can sgrin te bsgyur du ma btub /
NK032(khi)007:947: rnal 'byor pa gang gi blos bcos su med pas na ma bcos pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:948: ma bcos pa'i de nyid yid kyi yul la ma /
NK032(khi)007:951: bsam pa'i yul la mi gnas te /
NK032(khi)007:952: bsam du ma btub pas na bsam 'das so //
NK032(khi)007:953: bsam las 'das pa'i don de yang bsam pa dran
NK032(khi)007:954: pa blos brjod pa'i yul la mi gnas te smra
NK032(khi)007:955: ru ma btub pas na brjod med do //
NK032(khi)007:956: brjod du ma btub pa'i don de la dus gsum
NK032(khi)007:957: du 'gyur bar med par gnas pas na ngang zhes
NK032(khi)007:958: bya'o // la zhes pa ni yul du bstan pa'am
NK032(khi)007:959: gong gi brjod med la sogs pa'i yon tan nam
NK032(khi)007:960: don de las lhag pa med pas mthar thug pa
NK032(khi)007:961: bya'o // yin pas la'o // de la gzung 'dzin
NK032(khi)007:962: gyi bag chags mi gnas par phyag pa na phyag
NK032(khi)007:963: bya'o // yin pas la'o // ces bya'o // de
NK032(khi)007:964: lta bu'i don rtogs shing mngon du gyur pa des
NK032(khi)007:966: don de las lhag par bstan du med de /
NK032(khi)007:967: blo'i 'dod pa zad pas na lo zhes bya'o //
NK032(khi)007:968: des ni sngon du mchod brjod bstan no //
NK032(khi)007:969: gnyis pa bstan par dam bca' ba ni /
NK032(khi)007:970: chos gzhan gyi lugs su bshad par dam bca' ba zhes 'byung ba yin te /
NK032(khi)007:971: 'di ni chos spyi'i gnas lugs bshad pa lta bu ma yin pas /
NK032(khi)007:972: don rang gi mtshan nyid bla ma'i gdams ngag gis
NK032(khi)007:973: ngo sprad nas ston pa yin pas na dam bca'
NK032(khi)007:974: ba'o // de la gdod nas dag pa'i byang chub sems nyid kyis /
NK032(khi)007:975: nyid kyi ngo bo nyid kyi don bstan bya ba yin pas /
NK032(khi)007:976: gdod nas dag pa bya ba ni /
NK032(khi)007:977: sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs de la /
NK032(khi)007:978: ye gdod ma nas rnam rtog rang rgyud du grub
NK032(khi)007:979: pa rdul phra rab tsam gcig kyang mi gnas pas
NK032(khi)007:981: byang zhes pa ni sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs
NK032(khi)007:982: de la bag chags bzang ngan gang gis kyang ma
NK032(khi)007:983: bslad de / gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa mi gnas pas na byang pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:984: chub pa ni ye shes lnga dang ldan pa de /
NK032(khi)007:985: sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs chos bzhi dang ldan pa ni /
NK032(khi)007:986: ye nas dus gsum du 'du 'bral med par gnas
NK032(khi)007:987: pa de shes pas na chos kyi dbyings kyi ye
NK032(khi)007:988: shes / de rang gi rgyud la yod pa de
NK032(khi)007:989: rang du rig cing rang gsal bas na me long
NK032(khi)007:991: ya mtha' rgyal ba'i da la nas /
NK032(khi)007:992: ma mtha' dmyal ba'i grong khyer yan chad la che chung med /
NK032(khi)007:993: bzang ngan med par ye nas mnyam por khyab pa'i
NK032(khi)007:994: don de nyid shes pas na mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK032(khi)007:995: ye shes / de yang yod pa sems can kun gyi rgyud la yod /
NK032(khi)007:996: yin pa 'di ltar snang grags kyi chos thams cad wal le /
NK032(khi)007:998: de so so rang rang gi rgyud la rtogs su byung bas na so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK032(khi)007:999: de ltar du yin pa'i don de shes shing rtogs tsa na /
NK032(khi)007:1000: bya ba'i blo thams cad ma grub pas na bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK032(khi)007:1001: de ltar yang rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)007:1002: rang gsal ye nas ma bcos pa'i //
NK032(khi)007:1003: don de shes pas ye shes yin //
NK032(khi)007:1005: ye shes de yang sems kyi rnam par rtog pa ma yin te /
NK032(khi)007:1006: sems ma yin pa'i phyir na sems nyid yin te /
NK032(khi)007:1007: sems ma yin pa ni rnam par rtog pa ma yin te /
NK032(khi)007:1008: sems ma yin pa'i phyir na sems nyid yin te /
NK032(khi)007:1009: sems ma yin pa ni rnam par rtog pa med
NK032(khi)007:1010: cing 'gyur ba med pas na sems ma yin te
NK032(khi)007:1011: sems nyid do // de gzhan nas btsal ma dgos
NK032(khi)007:1012: par rang gi rgyud la yod pas na nyid kyi'o
NK032(khi)007:1013: sems nyid do // // ngo bo nyid ni sems
NK032(khi)007:1014: nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs ma bcos pa'i ngo bo
NK032(khi)007:1015: sems nyid do // // nyid do // de yang ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)007:1016: ngo bo nyid ni gnas lugs te //
NK032(khi)007:1018: don bstan pa zhes pa don gzhan gcig nas ston pa lta bu gcig med de /
NK032(khi)007:1019: rang gi rgyud la yod pa'i sems kyi don sngar
NK032(khi)007:1020: ma rtogs pa de bla ma'i brda' dang ngag gis
NK032(khi)007:1021: ngo sprad nas rig cing rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:1022: de yang tshul lam thabs ji lta bur rtogs na /
NK032(khi)007:1023: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid kyi don de /
NK032(khi)007:1024: bla ma'i brda' dang ngag gis stan gcig gi steng du rang gi rgyud la sbyar nas /
NK032(khi)007:1025: nyams su myong ba'i don de la yid ches shing /
NK032(khi)007:1026: the tshom mi za bar rtogs par bya ba'i don du /
NK032(khi)007:1027: man ngag lung dang mi 'gal bar ston pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:1028: slob dpon 'dzeng chen po'i zhal nas /
NK032(khi)007:1029: chos spyi'i rnam par shigs kyis bshig /
NK032(khi)007:1030: don rang gi mtshan nyid la 'ub kyisabsdusa nas /
NK032(khi)007:1031: sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs de bla ma'i brda'
NK032(khi)007:1032: dang ngag gis rang gi rgyud la 'char gyin sbyar
NK032(khi)007:1033: nas / man ngag lung dang mi 'gal bar ston pa ni /
NK032(khi)007:1034: gdams ngag che ba yin skad /
NK032(khi)007:1035: de yang gsang sngags don gyi tshad ma las /
NK032(khi)007:1036: lung dang man ngag gi don rang rig nges par 'char zhes bshad do //
NK032(khi)007:1037: de la chos spyi'i 'dod lugs ni /
NK032(khi)007:1038: ston pa rnam pa gsum gyis bstan pa'i chos yin te /
NK032(khi)007:1039: chos sku'i ston pa dpal kun tu bzang pos dbang po rab gsum la /
NK032(khi)007:1040: chos sde dang rgyud sde klong sde gsum bstan /
NK032(khi)007:1041: tshul lam thabs ji ltar bstan na byin gyis brlabs nas bstan /
NK032(khi)007:1043: sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la sems bya ba gcig yod de /
NK032(khi)007:1044: sems de yang ma rig pas de ma yin la
NK032(khi)007:1045: der 'dzin gyi shes pa log rtog 'khrul par 'dug
NK032(khi)007:1046: pas / de ma 'khrul par bya ba'i phyir chos sde bstan /
NK032(khi)007:1047: sems nyid de yang rgyun chad med par 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)007:1048: chos nyid kyang rgyun chad med par bya'i phyir rgyud sde bstan /
NK032(khi)007:1049: sems nyid de yang na yin par 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)007:1050: chos nyid kyang mi zad par bstan pa'i phyir klong sde bstan /
NK032(khi)007:1051: de yang bsdu na bslab pa rnam pa gsum du 'dus so //
NK032(khi)007:1052: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku'i ston pa dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis bstan pa'i 'bring gsum la /
NK032(khi)007:1053: chos kri ya yo ga u pa gsum bstan /
NK032(khi)007:1054: tshul lam thabs ji ltar bstan na thabs brdas bstan /
NK032(khi)007:1055: don gang la dgongs na lus ngag yid gsum 'dul ba la dgongs nas bstan /
NK032(khi)007:1056: de yang lus 'dul phyir kri ya /
NK032(khi)007:1059: de tsho yang bsdu na bslab pa gsum du 'dus so //
NK032(khi)007:1060: sprul pa sku'i ston pa sh+aakya thub pas /
NK032(khi)007:1061: bstan pa chos tha ma gsum la 'dul ba mngon pa mdo sde gsum bstan /
NK032(khi)007:1062: tshul lam thabs ji ltar bstan na /
NK032(khi)007:1064: don gang la dgongs nas bstan na /
NK032(khi)007:1065: sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la nyon mongs pa dug gsum yod pas de 'dul ba'i phyir gsungs /
NK032(khi)007:1066: de yang 'dod chags 'dul ba'i phyir 'dul ba bstan /
NK032(khi)007:1067: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i phyir mdo sde bstan /
NK032(khi)007:1068: gti mug 'dul ba'i phyir mngon pa bstan /
NK032(khi)007:1069: de dag gi brjod bya bslab pa gsum du 'dus so //
NK032(khi)007:1070: de ltar sku gsum gyis bstan pa'i chos gsum yang
NK032(khi)007:1071: gang zag dbang por rab 'bring tha ma gsum la
NK032(khi)007:1073: de yang nges brjod bla ma'i lung las /
NK032(khi)007:1074: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa' gsum //
NK032(khi)007:1075: bskal pa gsum gyis sangs rgyas sa la sleb //
NK032(khi)007:1076: kri ya u pa yo ga dag dang gsum //
NK032(khi)007:1077: mi tshe gsum gyis sangs rgyas sa la sbyor //
NK032(khi)007:1078: bskyed dang rdzogs dang rdzogs pa chen po gsum //
NK032(khi)007:1079: mi tshe gcig gis sangs rgyas lag gis len //
NK032(khi)007:1081: gang zag dbang po tha ma sprul sku'i bstan pas 'dul ba de cung zad gcig spro na /
NK032(khi)007:1082: dug gsum gyi gnyen po sde snod gsum las /
NK032(khi)007:1083: 'dod chags nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen por 'dul ba nyi khri chig stong gsungs /
NK032(khi)007:1084: zhe sdang nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen por mdo sde nyi khri chig stong gsungs /
NK032(khi)007:1085: gti mug nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen por mngon pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs /
NK032(khi)007:1086: dug gsum spyi mthun las gyur pa nyi khri chig
NK032(khi)007:1087: stong gi gnyen por sde snod gsum spyi mthun las
NK032(khi)007:1088: gyur pa'i chos kyi sgo mo nyi khri chig stong
NK032(khi)007:1089: gsungs so // de yang mdo bcu las /
NK032(khi)007:1091: zhe sdang 'dul phyir mdo sde gsungs //
NK032(khi)007:1092: gti mug 'dul phyir mngon pa gsungs //
NK032(khi)007:1093: dug gsum cha mnyam spyi mthun gnyen po ru //
NK032(khi)007:1094: sde snod gsum las cha mnyam spyi mthun gsungs pa lags //
NK032(khi)007:1096: de ltar chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong gnyen po'i don du gsungs /
NK032(khi)007:1097: rnam dbye yan lag bcu gnyis su gsungs te /
NK032(khi)007:1098: dbye ba'am spros pa'i don la dgongs te bka' stsal to //
NK032(khi)007:1100: 'bring du ni nyon mongs pa de dag kyang rnam
NK032(khi)007:1101: par dbye na ma rig pa nas rga shi'i bar
NK032(khi)007:1102: rten 'brel yan lag bcu gnyis su gnas pa las
NK032(khi)007:1103: / chos kyi sgo mo de dag kyang rnam bzhag
NK032(khi)007:1104: gi rnam dbye yan lag bcu gnyis su gsungs so
NK032(khi)007:1105: / // rgyas bsdus 'bring po'i don la dgongs te bka' stsal to //
NK032(khi)007:1107: nyon mongs pa de dag bsdu na /
NK032(khi)007:1108: ngo bo rang bzhin mtshan nyid gsum du 'dus /
NK032(khi)007:1109: de gsum ni ngo bo ma rig pa las byung /
NK032(khi)007:1111: mtshan nyid sdug bsngal du nyams su myong /
NK032(khi)007:1112: ngo bo ma rig pa de gti mug gi cha yin /
NK032(khi)007:1113: rang bzhin 'khrul pa de 'dod chags kyi cha yin /
NK032(khi)007:1114: mtshan nyid sdug bsngal de zhe sdang gi cha yin /
NK032(khi)007:1115: gnyen po chos kyi sgo mo de dag kyang bsdu na don bslab pa gsum du 'dus so //
NK032(khi)007:1116: lhag pa tshul khrims sems shes rab gsum du nyams su len pa las 'dul ba tshul khrims kyi /
NK032(khi)007:1118: mngon pa lhag pa shes rab bstan to //
NK032(khi)007:1119: de dag ni bsdu ba'i don la dgongs te bka' stsal to //
NK032(khi)007:1120: de rnams ni chos spyi'i rnam bzhag gam spyi'i 'dod lugs so //
NK032(khi)007:1121: don rang gi mtshan nyid 'di ru nye bar bsdu ba ni nyon mongs pa'i rtsa ba ngo bo /
NK032(khi)007:1123: mtshan nyid gsum rang gi rgyud la nye bar bsdu na /
NK032(khi)007:1124: sems nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i ngo bo chos sku'i rang bzhin yin pa /
NK032(khi)007:1125: de ma rtog pa'i ngo bo ma rig pa gti mug gi cha /
NK032(khi)007:1126: chos nyid ci yang ma yin pa la nga dang
NK032(khi)007:1127: bdag tu gzung zhing 'dzin pa'i bag chags gcig byung
NK032(khi)007:1128: ba de rang bzhin 'khrul pa yin te 'dod chags
NK032(khi)007:1129: kyi cha / don ma rig pa la ched du
NK032(khi)007:1130: 'dzin pa'i bag chags la brten nas chags sdang gi
NK032(khi)007:1131: kyi cha / mtshan nyid / sdug bsngal sna tshogs
NK032(khi)007:1132: su nyams su myong ba de mtshan nyid sdug bsngal
NK032(khi)007:1133: yin te zhe sdang gi cha yin /
NK032(khi)007:1134: de ltar yang rtsa rgyu ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)007:1135: rang gsal dgongs pa'i thugs ma rig /
NK032(khi)007:1136: 'dzin pa cha la gang gnas kyang //
NK032(khi)007:1139: chos sgo'i don bslab pa gsum rang gi rgyud la nye bar bsdu na /
NK032(khi)007:1140: sems nyid spros bral chos skur rig cing gsal ba de lhag pa shes rab /
NK032(khi)007:1141: de'i ngang la 'du byed kyi blo mi gnas pa de lhag pa tshul khrims /
NK032(khi)007:1142: de tsa na nyon mongs pa gang yang mi gnas
NK032(khi)007:1143: pas chos nyid dang mi 'bral ba de lhag pa
NK032(khi)007:1145: de ltar yang theg pa chen po rgyud bla ma las /
NK032(khi)007:1146: spros med rtogs pa shes rab ste //
NK032(khi)007:1147: 'du byed med pa tshul khrims yin //
NK032(khi)007:1148: gnas med mi 'bral bsam gtan mchog /
NK032(khi)007:1150: de ni don rang gi mtshan nyid 'dod pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:1151: gdams ngag 'di'i dbang du byas na /
NK032(khi)007:1152: man ngag lung dang mi 'gal bar ston pa las /
NK032(khi)007:1154: don rang gi mtshan nyid gnyis /
NK032(khi)007:1155: gnyis su med pa snying po'i don du lhan cig tu gnas pas /
NK032(khi)007:1156: sems nyid dngos po'i gshis kyi gnas lugs de gdan
NK032(khi)007:1157: gcig gi steng du bla ma'i brda' dang ngag gis
NK032(khi)007:1158: rgyud la sbyar bas gsal ba /
NK032(khi)007:1160: bde ba gsum ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa gcig rgyud la skye'o //
NK032(khi)007:1161: dbyer mi phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed bya ba'am /
NK032(khi)007:1162: mi phyed bya ba'i blo'i mtha' 'am /
NK032(khi)007:1163: tshig gi mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:1164: de tsa na gsal ba gnad kyi brda' yis nyon
NK032(khi)007:1165: mongs pa'i rtsa ba ma rig pa'i ngo bo dag
NK032(khi)007:1166: nas / rang rig rang gsal du gnas gyur pa de /
NK032(khi)007:1167: chos kyi sgo mo'i rtsa ba lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa /
NK032(khi)007:1168: mi rtog pa gnad kyi brda' yis rang bzhin 'khrul pa chod nas /
NK032(khi)007:1169: chos nyid mi rtog par gnas gyur pa de /
NK032(khi)007:1170: chos sgo'i rtsa ba lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa /
NK032(khi)007:1171: bde ba gnad kyi brda' yis mtshan nyid sdug bsngal zad nas mi gnas par /
NK032(khi)007:1172: zag med kyi bde bar gnas gyur pa de chos
NK032(khi)007:1173: kyi sgo mo'i rtsa ba lhag pa ting nge 'dzin
NK032(khi)007:1174: gyi bslab pa'o // de gsum tshig la tha dad
NK032(khi)007:1175: kyang don la dbyer mi phyed pa gcig rgyud la
NK032(khi)007:1176: shar ba de chos kyi dbyings so //
NK032(khi)007:1177: dbyer mi phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed bya ba'am /
NK032(khi)007:1178: mi phyed bya ba'i blo'i mtha'am /
NK032(khi)007:1179: tshig gi mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi
NK032(khi)007:1180: gnas pa de chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'o
NK032(khi)007:1181: // de yang ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)007:1182: bsam med mkha' gsang ye sangs rgyas //
NK032(khi)007:1185: de yang bla mas bstan te byung bas na chos kyi chos nyid /
NK032(khi)007:1186: rang gi nyams su myong bas na sems kyi sems nyid /
NK032(khi)007:1187: dpe nam mkha' lta bur 'dug pas na nam mkha'i mtshan nyid /
NK032(khi)007:1188: de gsum tshig la tha dad kyang don la gcig tu 'dug pas na /
NK032(khi)007:1189: nyid gsum gcig tu bsre ba 'di bzhag phyis mi len gyi dgongs pa zhes bya'o //
NK032(khi)007:1190: rnam smin gyi lus 'di bzhag nas /
NK032(khi)007:1191: phyi mar rang rgyud pa'i lus mi len par sangs rgya bar 'gyur bas so //
NK032(khi)007:1192: don de lta bu de ston pa bla ma'i brda' dang ngag gis ston /
NK032(khi)007:1193: lta ba rang gi rgyud la blta /
NK032(khi)007:1194: de bltas pa tsam gyis mi chog ste rtogs dgos /
NK032(khi)007:1195: rtogs pa tsam gyis mi chog ste rtogs pa mngon du gyur dgos pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:1196: de ltar rtogs te don mngon du gyur na /
NK032(khi)007:1197: nam gyur pa dang sangs rgyas pa de rang yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)007:1198: de ltar yang ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)007:1199: rtogs pa'i klong du gang 'dris pa //
NK032(khi)007:1200: mi zhes bya ba sangs rgyas yin //
NK032(khi)007:1201: rdo rje sems dpa' gud na med //
NK032(khi)007:1203: de ni snying po'i don la dgongs te bka' stsal pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:1204: de yang ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)007:1205: snying po'i don la bya ba med //
NK032(khi)007:1206: yid la mi byed rang bzhin gnas //
NK032(khi)007:1208: de ltar ngo bo ma rig pa /
NK032(khi)007:1211: bla ma'i gdams ngag gis bstan te ngo sprod nas gsal ba /
NK032(khi)007:1214: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa gcig tu rtogs tsa na /
NK032(khi)007:1215: dbyer mi phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed ces bya'am /
NK032(khi)007:1216: mi phyed bya ba'i blo'i mtha' 'am /
NK032(khi)007:1217: tshig gi mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas par dag tsa na /
NK032(khi)007:1218: sangs rgyas de nyid yin te /
NK032(khi)007:1219: rgyud brtag pa gnyis pa las /
NK032(khi)007:1220: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK032(khi)007:1221: 'on kyang glo bur dri mas bsgrib //
NK032(khi)007:1222: dri ma bsal na sangs rgyas nyid //
NK032(khi)007:1224: rna brgyud lung gi phreng ba las /
NK032(khi)007:1225: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten thams cad na //
NK032(khi)007:1226: sangs rgyas btsal bas mi rnyed de //
NK032(khi)007:1227: rang sems rtogs na sangs rgyas nyid //
NK032(khi)007:1228: de las gzhan du ma 'tshol cig /
NK032(khi)007:1230: ye shes gsang ba las kyang /
NK032(khi)007:1231: ye nas chos skur gnas pa la //
NK032(khi)007:1232: sangs rgyas gzhan nas ma 'tshol cig /
NK032(khi)007:1234: de rnams kyis chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid de /
NK032(khi)007:1235: bla ma'i brda' dang ngag gis so so rang rang gi rgyud la sbyar nas /
NK032(khi)007:1236: don nyams su myong zhing rtogs pa'i don de sangs
NK032(khi)007:1237: rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin par man ngag lung dang
NK032(khi)007:1239: de yang mdo sde nges par 'jog pa las /
NK032(khi)007:1240: dge sbyong chen po'i 'di skad gsungs //
NK032(khi)007:1241: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ste //
NK032(khi)007:1242: dge ba phun sum tshogs par spyad //
NK032(khi)007:1243: rang gi sems ni yongs su 'dul //
NK032(khi)007:1244: 'di ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK032(khi)007:1249: gsum gyi sdig pa ci yang mi byed /
NK032(khi)007:1251: bslab pa phun sum tshogs pa la longs spyod /
NK032(khi)007:1252: rang gi sems blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam la yang mi gnas par thul tsa na /
NK032(khi)007:1253: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa phyin ci ma log pa ste /
NK032(khi)007:1255: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa yin no //
NK032(khi)007:1256: de yan chad kyis sngon du mchod par brjod cing bstan par dam bca' ba bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)007:1257: bkra shis mtshan ldan ka p+aa la //
NK032(khi)007:1258: ka ni gang du mi gnas la //
NK032(khi)007:1259: p+aa ni skye ba med pa'i dbyings //
NK032(khi)007:1260: la ni blo yi yul las 'das //
NK032(khi)007:1261: sku gsum mi 'gyur ka p+aa lar //
NK032(khi)007:1262: skye shi med pa'i bdud rtsir sbyar //
NK032(khi)007:1264: bde ba chen po'i chang gis bran //
NK032(khi)007:1265: ma bcos 'gyur ba med par byin gyis brlabs //
NK032(khi)007:1266: nyes pa med par mang du spel //
NK032(khi)007:1267: zhen pa med par dbyings su 'bul //
NK032(khi)007:1268: re dogs med par bzhes su gsol //
NK032(khi)007:1270: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK032(khi)007:1272: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i dkar chag bzhugs /
NK032(khi)007:1273: ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK032(khi)007:1274: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa 'di la chos skor gyi grangs nges 'di rnams bdog ste /
NK032(khi)007:1275: gzhung dang yig sna'i skor dang /
NK032(khi)007:1276: byin rlabs dbang gi skor dang /
NK032(khi)007:1277: sgom sgrub nyams len gyi skor dang /
NK032(khi)007:1278: zhal gdams man ngag gi skor dang bzhi'o //
NK032(khi)007:1279: dang po la rtsa ba rdo rje'i tshig lam dang gcig /
NK032(khi)007:1280: de'i gsal byed kyi yig sna dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)007:1281: de'i skabs sbyor lhan thabs dang gsum mo //
NK032(khi)007:1282: gnyis pa la sngon 'gro chos spyod kyi rim pa dang /
NK032(khi)007:1283: dbang dngos la sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs dang /
NK032(khi)007:1284: lar dbang rgyas bsdus rim pa gsum mo //
NK032(khi)007:1285: gsum pa la sgom pa dang /
NK032(khi)007:1288: sgom pa la khrid yig rgyas bsdus 'bring gsum mo //
NK032(khi)007:1289: sgrub pa la mngon rdzogs yab yum gyi sgrub yig dang /
NK032(khi)007:1290: d+aa ki gsang spyod sgrub pa dang /
NK032(khi)007:1291: d+aa ki mkha' spyod kyi sgrub pa dang /
NK032(khi)007:1292: d+aa ki sde gsum gyi longs spyod rgyas pa'i sgrub pa dang /
NK032(khi)007:1293: chos 'di'i bka' srung la d+aa ki ma mngon spyod kyi sgrub pa dang /
NK032(khi)007:1294: sgom sgrub kyi cha lag tu bcud len gyi skor ro //
NK032(khi)007:1295: bzhi pa la zhal gdams phyi nang gsang gsum /
NK032(khi)007:1296: phyi ltar na zam chung bsdus pa dang /
NK032(khi)007:1297: snyan brgyud nyams kyi phreng ba dang /
NK032(khi)007:1298: rtsod zlog lung gi tshad ma dang gsum mo //
NK032(khi)007:1305: gsang ba ltar na 'pho ba gsum gyi zhal gdams /
NK032(khi)007:1306: sangs rgyas tshul bzhi'i zhal gdams /
NK032(khi)007:1307: don bsdus pa'i snying po gsum gyi zhal gdams so //
